parameters: ....A year ago, there was a great war between humans and monsters.

Amidst the world engulfed in war, the army led by the Hero
somehow managed to repel the evil monsters led by the Demon King.
At the cost of the Hero's life.......

However, for some reason, they were unable to fully suppress the
monsters. And due to the fact that more monsters than expected
attacked with clever tactics using their knowledge, nearly 30% of
the world remained invaded by the Demon King's army and entered a
ceasefire.

\F[1]\AA[F]The protagonist of this story is this girl. Her name
is Celia.

\F[1]\AA[F]This is a story set one year after Celia, who was
driven out of her hometown due to the effects of the war,
migrated to a certain town.

This is the story of her own unique battle against the new
war───────....
Celia \F[1]\AA[F]......sigh. When will I say it....

I was waiting for the right timing to say something 'very
important' in my life.

Celia \F[1]\AA[F]Hayato! After visiting the grave, we're going to
the priest's place.

\F[1]\AA[F]He is Hayato. He's been kinder to me than anyone else
since I came to town.

\F\c\AA[F]\c[14]This town is my birthplace\c[0], but for me, who had
been living in the city since I was conscious, it was a
completely unfamiliar place.

\F[1]\AA[F]I ended up drifting to such a hometown as a post-war
immigrant....., but thanks to Hayato, I was able to fit in
quickly.

Celia (Originally, I have a difficult personality, and I've
caused him a lot of trouble....) Well, let's go.

Celia | ....She seems to be talking to someone. I wonder if she's
busy?
| ....Huh? You're saying she's a beautiful person?

Something 'very important' in life.... That's about
\c[27]confession\c[0].

The reason I can live so easily now is thanks to Hayato. That's
why I want to convey my feelings....but....

Celia What if he dislikes me! What if he says, You've suddenly
become strange! What should I do!!

So time passed without me being able to say anything... it's
already been a month. What should I do? This is just like the
pattern of a hopelessly clumsy girl...

Celia \F[1]\AA[F] Ah, ah, that's right. Anyway, I had some
business at the church.

Celia \F[1]\AA[F] But she seemed busy, so maybe I'll come back
later. I left something at the church though....

Celia \F[1]\AA[F] Eh, speaking of which, were you talking with
the priest earlier...?
Celia Could it be... a monster\c[27]\c[0]?

Celia Well, that's impossible. You were just chatting with the
priest, so it should be fine.
